data.content:
**Summary of the fix:**

In MSTest v4, `Assert.IsInstanceOfType<T>(obj, out var typed)` was replaced with a return-value API:

```csharp
// Before (v3) — out parameter
Assert.IsInstanceOfType<MyType>(obj, out var typed);

// After (v4) — return value
var typed = Assert.IsInstanceOfType<MyType>(obj);
```

The assertion still validates the type and throws on failure, but now returns the cast value directly. I also updated your package from `3.8.0` → `4.1.0`. The project builds cleanly.
